\id 3JN - Indian Revised Version (IRV) Nagamese 
\h 3 John 
\toc1 John Laga Tritio Chithi 
\toc2 Third John 
\toc3 3Jn 
\mt1 John Laga Tritio Chithi 
\c 1  
\s1 Salam Kotha 
\p  
\v 1 Bura manu pora morom thaka Gaius ekjon cholawta ke likhi ase, kunke moi hosa pora morom kore. 
\p  
\v 2 Morom laga bhai, Moi prathana kore tumi logote sob bhal thakibo aru tumi laga gaw bhi bhal thakibo, tumi laga atma bhal kori kene thaka nisena.  
\v 3 Kelemane moi khushi pai jitia bhai khan ahi kene tumi hosa te berai thaka laga gawahi diye, tumi hosa te berai thaka nisena.  
\v 4 Moi etu pora aru dangor khushi nai, jitia ami laga bacha khan\f + \fr 1.4 \ft John laga chela khan koi ase.\f* hosa rasta te berai ase koi kene moi hune. 
\s1 Modot Aru Birodh Kora 
\p  
\v 5 Morom laga bhai, tumi biswas pora ki kori ase etu tumi bhai khan nimite aru bahar manu khan nimite kori ase  
\v 6 kun pora tumikhan laga morom kora laga gawahi girja manu khan laga usorte dise. Isor laga usorte bhal mohima hobole nimite tumi manu ke bhal pora saikene taikhan ke safar kori bole pathai dibi,  
\v 7 kelemane Isor laga naam nimite taikhan ulaikene jaise, aru Porjati manu khan pora eku luwa nai.  
\v 8 Amikhan bhi taikhan ke mati bole lage, etu pora amikhan bhi hosa te kaam kora sathi hoi jabo. 
\p  
\v 9 Moi manu khan\f + \fr 1.9 \ft Girja laga manu khan, biswasi khan ke chithi likha koi ase.\f* nimite kiba likhise, kintu Diotrephes, kun manu laga age te thaki bole nimite bhal pai, tai amikhan ke swekar nakore.  
\v 10 Jodi moi ahe, Moi tai ki kaam kori ase etu sabo, amikhan laga bhirodh te biya kotha kori ase. Kintu eneka kori kene bhi khushi panai, tai nijor pora bhi bhai kokai khan ke mati bole mon nai, aru kun manu ke mati bole mon kore taikhan ke rukhai diye aru girja laga bahar\f + \fr 1.10 \ft Girja laga biswasi manu laga ginti pora naam ulai diya.\f* te ulai diye.  
\v 11 Morom laga bhai, biya kaam khan nokoribi kintu ki to bhal kaam ase etu he koribi. Kun manu bhal kaam kore tai Isor laga ase; aru kun manu biya kaam kore tai Isor ke dikha nai.  
\v 12 Demetrius ke sob manu pora aru hosa pora tai nijor laga gawahi diye. Kintu amikhan bhi gawahi diye, aru tumikhan jane amikhan laga gawahi to hosa ase. 
\s1 Hekh Salam 
\p  
\v 13 Moi tumikhan ke bisi kotha likhi bole ase, kintu moi kolom aru siyahi pora etu kotha khan tumikhan ke likhi bole mon nai.  
\v 14 Kintu moi tumikhan ke joldi lok pabole itcha kori ase, titia moi khan ekjon-ekjon logote bohi kene kotha koribo.  
\v 15 Tumikhan logote shanti thaki bole dibi. Sathi khan bhi tumikhan ke salam di ase. Naam loi kene ta te thaka sathi khan ke salam di dibi\f + \fr 1.15 \ft 2 John 1:12.\f*.